    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers exceptional throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and remains planted thanks to a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure for this chassis. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Recent service includes a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rod bearing replacement to maintain the integrity of the 8,000 RPM redline. While the aesthetics reflect its status as a driven enthusiast's car, the suspension geometry and powertrain harmonics are dialed for peak performance.",
